{"tid":143140,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［長文］頭先同條女食飯 我讚個鬼佬佢竟然聽唔明","createTime":"2017-03-04T11:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T13:36:22.000Z","uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c77896b5cc733bcaf90b9d1332ff34b0adf396a","tid":143140,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:29:04.000Z","msg":"本來今日條女生日 比佢話事揀去邊到食飯 今次仲要係我請 <br />\n<br />\n條仆街就揀左間好撚貴既西餐廳 我都唔撚識讀間餐廳既名 我見一塊死人扒都成幾百蚊 <br />\n<br />\n但見條女生日 好 今日我忍9你 <br />\n<br />\n入到去 我就同女朋友坐左係個卡位到 個WAITER(鬼佬)走埋黎問:what can I help you? <br />\n<br />\n雖然我英文真係中一二程度 不過喱句都唔算難到我 <br />\n<br />\n我女朋友用英文話 想要拎個MENU睇睇 <br />\n<br />\n由於入面全部英文我都唔多識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我就話跟女朋友點餐 佢要咩我要咩就算 <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬又走番埋黎問左句野 我剩係聽到:what xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx like? <br />\n<br />\n我女友就點左2個DINNER SPECIAL 之後個鬼佬又問:what xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx? <br />\n<br />\n我仍然係聽唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女友就同佢講:WELL DONE! <br />\n<br />\n我聽到喱到我大約就GET到 我估個鬼佬問佢覺得喱間餐廳既質素/員工服務/態度點 因為我見女友都讚佢 <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬轉另轉頭問我:whatxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx? <br />\n<br />\n我好自豪 充滿自信 大大聲答: GOOD JOB!! <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬就呆哂 唔明我無啦啦做乜講GOOD JOB咁 <br />\n<br />\n女友見到 即刻幫我答:WELL DONE <br />\n<br />\n個鬼佬點點頭 就行左去 我其實到而家都唔明白 到底讚外國人係咪一定要用WELL DONE? <br />\n<br />\n點解講GOOD JOB佢反而又呆哂又聽唔到咁既???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇巴打可以幫幫手教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830c63fb54d90abe61d7f070c23fea772e550302","tid":143140,"uid":16034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔掂 返去作過啦"},{"pid":"84cc49dca43636789f2c457242031861036149fd","tid":143140,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔掂 返去作過啦</blockquote><br />\n真人真事呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2aa46aa340a9661591b74ea45186771e304216","tid":143140,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:38:35.000Z","msg":"連登仔呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55291e58d510b82e1d5716d7d795300c32f165d2","tid":143140,"uid":33650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5d9dbc410dca5754760566866b45f2b8e6b406","tid":143140,"uid":34742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:39:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd36f7e3934eb7b9cff30769d0436558efca958d","tid":143140,"uid":16283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:39:45.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗咁快又回帶..."},{"pid":"41655a7c090d145bd0ef25daf1022b37a4acd95b","tid":143140,"uid":5852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:39:52.000Z","msg":"好似要搭excellent先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc077e7de9ab2c8c4dd0812a67639030a5447976","tid":143140,"uid":5852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似要<span style=\"color: red;\">搭</span>excellent先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n答"},{"pid":"467f3f415e95eeb780007941ffb6704190533921","tid":143140,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:41:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n回乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e905b930cf88a8979816d3b08011b50f23873d","tid":143140,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T11:41:24.000Z","msg":"準備blo